title: Murray, Carroll lead Eagles to 27-7 win over Giants
text:
> Pennsylvania Murray, Carroll lead Eagles to 27-7 win over Giants Philadelphia Eagles wide receiver Josh Huff, left, tries to avoid a hit by New York Giants strong safety Brandon Meriweather during the first half of an NFL football game, Monday, Oct. 19, 2015, in Philadelphia.
